public class TranscoderWrapperStatisticsSupport
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.spy.memcached.transcoders.Transcoder<java.lang.Object>

A Transcoder that delegates all calls to a provided delegate. For encode(Object) additionally the size of the encoded data is stored in the Statistics.getCachedDataSizeProbe().

See Also:
CachedData.getData(), Statistics.MinMaxAvgProbe.register(long)
